Coil Tubing Operator
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/04/29 13:07:53
Ref. JB3045473
Job Description
Carries out a variety of skilled activities related to operations of coil tubing equipment on assigned well site. Includes running in-hole coil tubing string in accordance with well program, preparing equipment and securing well head equipment, maintaining CT operations safe and within given parameters to avoid breakage or interruption. Carries our routine maintenance on assigned equipment and report any malfunction thereon, observe field services procedures and implements as approved by Company management
Skills
Diploma Holder
Training courses related to coil tubing operations
